## Application container for the Cure colony example.
##
## The compiler verifies that exactly one `app` container exists in
## the project and that its name matches `[application].name` in
## `Cure.toml`. The `root = sup Colony` line wires the application's
## `start/2` callback to the `Colony` supervisor declared in
## `colony.cure`.

app CureColony
  vsn         = "0.1.0"
  description = "Cure colony showcase: a typed supervision tree"
  root        = sup Colony
